item.title: About Myself
item.description: Hello! I’m currently a student at Cal State University, Chico pursuing a Bachelor of Science in Mathematics with a focus in Statistics. I had started out at Sierra Community College in 2015 as a Business major, eventually switching to Accounting and then Computer Science, and finally transferring to Chico State in the Fall of 2019 where I once again changed my major (fourth times the charm) from CS to Mathematics and I’ve loved it ever since.
